	(text "The trigger input network high pass fitlers the input signal to limit the pulsewidth\nat the BJT base to ~10µs. This is to prevent damage to the system from sustained\ninput signals that keep the BJT turned on. The additional diode limits reverse voltage\nat the base that happens when the trigger signal goes from high to low."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
